        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"z05-feature-shell\"><section class=\"z05-section dark z05-gallery-section\"><div class=\"z05-wrap\"><div class=\"z05-gallery-head\"><p class=\"z05-kicker\">Listening Notes</p><h2>What you notice when it is in hand</h2><p class=\"z05-gallery-lead\">A few close looks at the parts that change daily listening: the AuAg faceplates, the physical TwinCore switch, the cable system, and the tips that keep the seal honest.</p></div><div class=\"z05-gallery-grid\"><figure tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" class=\"feature\"><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-forged-carbon-faceplate-hero.jpg' | asset_img_url: '1200x' }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg main faceplate hero image\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>AuAg faceplates</b><span>Gold on one side, silver on the other. It is the kind of finish you keep turning under the light before the first track even starts.</span></figcaption></figure><figure tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-twincore-switch-closeup.jpg' | asset_img_url: '1200x' }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg TwinCore switch close-up\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>TwinCore switch</b><span>A real switch for real mood changes: more body when you want to sink in, more bite when you want to listen closer.</span></figcaption></figure><figure tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-swappable-cable-terminations.jpg' | asset_img_url: '1200x' }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg cable and swappable terminations\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>Cable kit</b><span>Phone, dongle, DAP, desktop chain. The included terminations cover the sources most of us actually rotate through.</span></figcaption></figure><figure tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-liquidmorph-accessory-tray.jpg' | asset_img_url: '1200x' }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg LiquidMorph eartip tray\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>LiquidMorph tips</b><span>Tip rolling is not decoration here. A better seal means steadier bass, cleaner center image, and less fiddling mid-album.</span></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"z05-lightbox\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><button class=\"z05-lightbox-close\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Close image preview\">×</button><figure><img src=\"\" alt=\"\"><figcaption><b></b><span></span></figcaption></figure></div></div></section></div><script>(function(){function initZ05GalleryLightbox(){document.querySelectorAll('.z05-gallery-section').forEach(function(section){if(section.dataset.lightboxReady)return;section.dataset.lightboxReady='true';var lightbox=section.querySelector('.z05-lightbox');if(!lightbox)return;var lightImg=lightbox.querySelector('img');var lightTitle=lightbox.querySelector('figcaption b');var lightText=lightbox.querySelector('figcaption span');var close=lightbox.querySelector('.z05-lightbox-close');var lastTrigger=null;function openLightbox(figure){lastTrigger=figure;var img=figure.querySelector('img');var title=figure.querySelector('figcaption b');var text=figure.querySelector('figcaption span');lightImg.src=img.currentSrc||img.src;lightImg.alt=img.alt||'';lightTitle.textContent=title?title.textContent:'';lightText.textContent=text?text.textContent:'';lightbox.classList.add('is-open');lightbox.setAttribute('aria-hidden','false');document.documentElement.classList.add('z05-lightbox-open');close.focus();}function closeLightbox(){lightbox.classList.remove('is-open');lightbox.setAttribute('aria-hidden','true');document.documentElement.classList.remove('z05-lightbox-open');lightImg.removeAttribute('src');if(lastTrigger)lastTrigger.focus();}section.querySelectorAll('.z05-gallery-grid figure').forEach(function(figure){figure.addEventListener('click',function(){openLightbox(figure);});figure.addEventListener('keydown',function(event){if(event.key==='Enter'||event.key===' '){event.preventDefault();openLightbox(figure);}});});close.addEventListener('click',closeLightbox);lightbox.addEventListener('click',function(event){if(event.target===lightbox)closeLightbox();});document.addEventListener('keydown',function(event){if(event.key==='Escape'&&lightbox.classList.contains('is-open'))closeLightbox();});});}if(document.readyState==='loading')document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',initZ05GalleryLightbox);else initZ05GalleryLightbox();})();</script>",
