    "z05_fitment": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"z05-feature-shell\"><section class=\"z05-section z05-fitment-section\"><div class=\"z05-wrap\"><div class=\"z05-fitment-head\"><div><p class=\"z05-kicker\">Fitment</p><h2>A universal fit that still feels settled</h2></div><p>The best tuning falls apart if the shell keeps shifting. Z05 AuAg keeps the body compact, routes the cable over-ear, and lets the tip do the sealing work.</p></div><div class=\"z05-fitment-showcase\"><figure class=\"z05-fitment-image\"><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-male-fitment.jpg' | asset_img_url: '1200x' }}\" alt=\"Adult male wearing Z05 AuAg universal in-ear monitor with over-ear cable\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>Real-world fit check</b><span>The cable takes the strain, the shell sits close, and the tip keeps the bass from wandering.</span></figcaption></figure><div class=\"z05-fitment-panel\"><article><span>Over-ear route</span><h3>Cable stays put</h3><p>Less tug at the shell when you move, sit, or swap sources.</p></article><article><span>Compact body</span><h3>No custom mold needed</h3><p>A small universal body that sits naturally instead of trying to fill the whole ear.</p></article><article><span>Seal support</span><h3>LiquidMorph tips</h3><p>LiquidMorph tips help lock in bass pressure and center image.</p></article></div></div></div></section></div>",
