    "z05_engineering": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div id=\"z05-engineering\" class=\"z05-feature-shell\"><section class=\"z05-section dark z05-engineering-section\"><div class=\"z05-wrap\"><div class=\"z05-engineering-head\"><div><p class=\"z05-kicker\">Craft & Sound</p><h2>Made to be worn, then looked at twice</h2></div><div class=\"z05-engineering-copy\"><p>The shell has to disappear before the finish gets to show off. Z05 AuAg starts with a compact universal fit, repeatable seal, and a driver layout that can stay convincing across long sessions.</p><p>The forged-carbon look is on the faceplates. The body is a 3D-printed shell, then each pair is dressed by hand with gold and silver foil work. It takes hours because the finish has to feel intentional, not sprinkled on.</p></div></div><div class=\"z05-craft-strip\" aria-label=\"Z05 AuAg craft notes\"><article><span>Faceplate</span><b>Forged carbon with Au/Ag foil</b></article><article><span>Shell body</span><b>3D-printed universal monitor shell</b></article><article><span>Finish time</span><b>Hand-laced over hours per pair</b></article></div><div class=\"z05-engineering-body\"><div class=\"z05-build-card z05-engineering-specs\"><strong>AAW Z05 AuAg</strong><dl><dt>Format</dt><dd>Universal-fit hybrid in-ear monitor</dd><dt>Low End</dt><dd>10mm PET diaphragm dynamic woofer</dd><dt>Clarity</dt><dd>Mid and super-high BA drivers for vocal edge and air</dd><dt>Voice Control</dt><dd>TwinCore physical voicing switch</dd><dt>Pressure Flow</dt><dd>Bass-Flow vent pressure system</dd><dt>Recommended Drive</dt><dd>20mW+ at 32Ohm; low or medium gain recommended</dd><dt>Recommended Source</dt><dd>Low-output-impedance source below 1Ohm: USB-C dongle, DAP, or compact DAC/amp</dd><dt>Approx. Weight</dt><dd>About 6g per earpiece, 12g per pair without cable</dd><dt>Finish</dt><dd>Forged-carbon faceplates; 3D-printed shells with hand-laced gold and silver foil finish</dd><dt>In The Box</dt><dd>2-pin detachable cable, 3.5mm, 4.4mm balanced, Type-C terminations, carrying case, LiquidMorph eartips</dd><dt>Warranty</dt><dd>1-year warranty</dd></dl></div><figure class=\"z05-engineering-hero\"><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-luxury-shell-geometry.jpg' | asset_img_url: '1200x' }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg shells in a minimalist luxury studio setting\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>Shell form, finish, and fit</b><span>The finish catches the eye; the compact shell shape is what lets you keep listening.</span></figcaption></figure></div></div></section></div>",
