    "z05_liquidmorph": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"z05-feature-shell\"><section class=\"z05-section z05-liquidmorph-section\"><div class=\"z05-wrap\"><div class=\"z05-liquidmorph-head\"><div><p class=\"z05-kicker\">Seal & Comfort</p><h2>The tip is part of the tuning</h2></div><p>With a dynamic woofer, seal is not a footnote. When the tip sits right, bass weight, vocal center, and left-right balance stop changing every time you move.</p></div><div class=\"z05-liquidmorph-showcase\"><figure class=\"z05-liquidmorph-primary\"><img src=\"{{ 'z05-liquidmorph-clear-eartips-closeup.jpg' | asset_img_url: '1200x' }}\" alt=\"LiquidMorph clear eartips with teal inner bore\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>Clear outer form, teal inner bore</b><span>Soft enough for comfort, structured enough to keep the bore stable.</span></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"z05-liquidmorph-tray\"><img src=\"{{ 'z05-auag-liquidmorph-accessory-tray.jpg' | asset_img_url: '1200x' }}\" alt=\"Z05 AuAg LiquidMorph eartip tray\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption><b>Size tray within reach</b><span>Because the right tip is often the difference between 'good' and 'there it is.'</span></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"z05-fit-panel\"><article><span>Clear flange</span><b>Rounded, transparent silicone that settles without feeling bulky.</b></article><article><span>Teal bore</span><b>A steadier inner path so the low end does not collapse when the shell shifts.</b></article><article><span>Size tray</span><b>Easy tip checks before a long session, not a loose bag of parts.</b></article></div></div></section></div>",
