    "z05_brand_trust": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"z05-feature-shell\"><section id=\"z05-built-by-aaw\" class=\"z05-section dark z05-brand-trust\"><div class=\"z05-wrap z05-brand-trust-inner\"><div class=\"z05-brand-trust-lead\"><p class=\"z05-kicker\">Built by AAW</p><h2><a href=\"/pages/about-us\">Advanced AcousticWerkes</a></h2><p class=\"z05-brand-trust-slogan\">Those who listen will find the way.</p></div><div class=\"z05-brand-trust-copy\"><p>Advanced AcousticWerkes, known as AAW, is a Singapore-based in-ear monitor specialist founded in 2014 by Kevin Wang. From its early custom IEM work to hybrid, electrostatic, planar, isobaric, and modular-fit designs, AAW has built its reputation around one principle: sound is engineered by listening. Every monitor brings together acoustic design, driver integration, ergonomic fit, digital modeling, and hand finishing to create an IEM that feels as considered as it sounds.</p><p>Z05 AuAg continues that lineage in a compact universal form: dynamic-driver body, balanced-armature detail, Bass-Flow pressure control, TwinCore two-mode voicing, and source-ready cabling for the way people actually listen today.</p><p><a class=\"z05-btn secondary\" href=\"/pages/about-us\">About Us</a></p></div></div></section></div>",
